<opener><salute>Celeberrimo, Doctissimoque Viro
      <lb/><choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>P.</abbr><expan>Petrus</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>A.</abbr><expan>Antonius</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p>Ex <choice><sic>nuperimis</sic><corr>nuperrimis</corr></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimi Filii Tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Danielis</rs> <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">Lite<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris</rs><note type="editorial">DIESER Brief ist von Daniel I B. an Michelotti ist nicht erhalten. =&gt; Ist noch im BIBB zu erfassen mit Systemnummer als nachgewiesener Brief. Im Briefinventar ist nur ein Brief 000055242 vom 16. Januar 1723 erhalten, der gedruckt wurde.</note>, Te esse san<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, et bene valere magna cum vo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>luptate intellexi; pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tereaque ingenii illius ipsius
      <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">tui Filii</rs> vim pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clare intellexi. Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> enim de famosissimi
      <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117584363" type="person">Bellini</rs> de missione sanguinis doctrina, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de ratione
      <lb/>solvendi problema Bellinian<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pertinens ad inveniend<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> quanti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> sanguinis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in statu naturali sine l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sione
      <lb/>viri<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> mitti potest: qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, inquam, de istiusmodi rebus
      <lb/>id<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filius tuus</rs> ad me perscripsit subtilissimo, feracissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo ingenio ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> jam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> esse pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissime demonstrant, mihique spem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>bent maiora in
      <lb/>poster<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ab illo expectandi. Utinam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> mecum ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nire vellet ibid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> per ann<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, aut per bienni<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> meis in lari<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus commoraturus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>grorum meor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> videndor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> gratia.
      <lb/>Hac enim ratione multum ab ipso meis in studiis adiuvari
      <lb/>possem. Post octo, aut nov<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> dies hinc disced<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> cum <choice><abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice>
<lb/>atque <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Laurentio Theupolo</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Argentorat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> profectu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rus. Si tempus permittet <choice><sic>Argenterota</sic><corr><rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Argentorato</rs></corr></choice> isthuc petam Te
      <lb/>Tuosque <choice><abbr>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clariss.<hi rend="sup">os</hi></abbr><expan>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissimos</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-118656503" type="persons">Filios</rs>, nec non <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Tuum</rs>
<lb/>salutandi causa. Defer<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> simul libror<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, quos ad Te mittit
      <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> atque <choice><abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>ingeniosissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119062372" type="person">Varignonus</rs>, exemplaria simul cum
      <lb/>instrumentis mathematicis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ut emer<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> mandasti in <rs key="B_1722-10-08_991170516664005501" type="letter">epis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tola</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Pierre Varignon vom 8. Oktober 1722 (ev. Prüfen, sehr wahrscheinlich ist es aber dieser Brief!).</note> ad ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>Doctissimum</expan></choice> meique Amicissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119062372" type="person">Varignon<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>. Quod si
      <lb/>non possem isthuc contendere efficiam ut celebris Anatomi<pb facs="1079328" n="2"/>cus <rs key="pers_DE-588-128382058" type="person">Saltzmannus</rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Argentorati</rs> adibo, occasione aliqua
      <lb/>peropportuna sese offerente, commemorata exemplaria
      <lb/>atque instrumenta in rebus <choice><sic>mathematcis</sic><corr>mathematicis</corr></choice> utilia ad Te trans<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mittat. Quod reliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est Te rogo, atque obtestor Vir
      <lb/>Illustrissime ut illa ipsa instrumenta mathematica
      <lb/>(qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ali<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>s h<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c veneunt <hi rend="u">un Louis d'or</hi> uti Galli loquuntur) ac<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cipere velis tanqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> munuscul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, quod grati animi testificandi
      <lb/>ergo Tibi offero. Memor sum, semperque ero beneficior<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
      <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te acceptor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, Tibique plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> me debere fateor eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
      <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> argento, quod pluries in accipiendis, et mittendis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> me
      <lb/>litteris erogare debuisti. Si in poster<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ad meas literas res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pondere non recusabis, et me plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> obstringes, et sumptus
      <lb/>omnes me persolutur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sancte polliceor. Maxime aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> inter om<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nia peto responsion<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ad me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs key="B_1722-01-23_991170515149605501" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli vom 23. Januar 1722</note> mense Januario
      <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito ad Te dat<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> obiectionesque <choice><abbr>Ill.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Com.</abbr><expan>Comitis</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccati</rs> complec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">corollario</rs><note type="editorial">werktag: newtonbhbd für die 1713er-Ausgabe der Principia schon eingesetzt, ABER: Hier wird spezifisch auf das 2. Corrolar verwiesen. Wäre das auszuweisen? Bibliogr. Angabe: Newton, Isaac, Philosophiae naturalis principia mathematica. Editio secunda auctior et emendatior, Cantabrigiae [Cambridge] (C. Crownfield) 1713. Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoniano</rs>, quod fals<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> esse conve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nit eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>ingeniosissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119062372" type="person">Varignonus</rs> utrique nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> communi
      <lb/>amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vinculo devinctus.<note type="editorial">Riccati-Kontroverse</note> <choice><sic>Argenteroto</sic><corr><rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Argentorato</rs></corr></choice> ad Te <rs key="B_1722-11-11_991170515148905501" type="letter">literas</rs><note type="editorial">Einen ersten Brief aus Strassburg (Argentoratum) schickt Michelotti am 11. November 1722 an Johann I Bernoulli, am selben Tag verfasst er einen <rs key="B_1722-11-11_991170515148805501" type="letter">zweiten kurzen Brief auf Französisch</rs> und legt diesem einen Brief an Tiepolos Bruder bei, um ihm über die zunehmenden Schmerzen Tiepolos zu berichten.</note> mitt<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
      <lb/>si isthuc Te salutat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> venire nequibo, deque mei itineris
      <lb/>ratione Te certior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> faciam ut possis aliquid mihi imperare,
      <lb/>quod maxime aveo.</p> <closer><salute>Vale plurimum Vir Amicissime
      <lb/>atque <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nobilissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Agnatum</rs>, nec non pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimos <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-118656503" type="persons">Filios</rs>
<lb/>duos meo nomine saluta.</salute>
<dateline>Dab<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a.</abbr><expan>ante</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>diem</expan></choice> 21 Octo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bris 1722.</dateline></closer>
